{"tid":1571182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"入閘機有部份零件倉庫存量不足","createTime":"2019-09-15T10:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T14:02:52.000Z","uid":136683,"like":389,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"544cd650b35a0881db90d0ec86a496ba12410cfd","tid":1571182,"uid":136683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:53:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/375050/逃犯條例-輕鐵售票機無被破壞卻封起-消息-僅餘少量零件更換\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F375050%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%BC%95%E9%90%B5%E5%94%AE%E7%A5%A8%E6%A9%9F%E7%84%A1%E8%A2%AB%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E5%8D%BB%E5%B0%81%E8%B5%B7-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E5%83%85%E9%A4%98%E5%B0%91%E9%87%8F%E9%9B%B6%E4%BB%B6%E6%9B%B4%E6%8F%9B&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXeedgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=1737ec1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/375050/逃犯條例-輕鐵售票機無被破壞卻封起-消息-僅餘少量零件更換</a><br />\n反修訂《逃犯條例》爭議持續逾3個月，8月起一連串示威遊行觸發的警民衝突，多次波及港鐵，多個港鐵站及輕鐵站的設施遭受破壞，包括閉路電視、入閘機及售票機等。港鐵其後以黑膠袋、紙盒及保鮮紙等密封相關設施，並貼上「暫停使用」字句。<br />\n<br />\n有港鐵消息人士透露，鑑於港鐵不希望再有設施被破壞，故輕鐵網絡的部分售票機即使沒有損毀亦被密封，僅維持有限度服務。港鐵回覆《香港01》表示，受損設施數量龐大，將採取不同措施，包括靈活調配不同車站設施及零件，讓工作人員作維修之用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=362808&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362808%26refer%3D&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXeedgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=afdb8f02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362808%26refer%3D&h=a673f324\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=362808&amp;refer=</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】鐵路工會聯合會主席林偉強出席電台節目時指，港鐵增聘尼泊爾籍人士監察有否乘客「逃票」，他不擔心會有衝突。<br />\n<br />\n另外，多個港鐵站遭破壞仍未全部復修，林偉強解釋除人手不足問題，零件亦短缺，如入閘機有部份零件倉庫存量不足，需由其他車站調配，強調職員已盡力搶修。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>你地係咪痴線架，拆到港鐵無料整返啲閘機，如果再拆落去，想俾錢入閘都唔得</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f28f3e368b805ae02dc219eaf7f0e62239f3341f","tid":1571182,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e8a2c52cd2f527bf425c4a126da46bc512f81d","tid":1571182,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:57:06.000Z","msg":"只有一個方法可以有效打擊藍屍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570141</a>"},{"pid":"89278d5121192a93eeebcee0849b8af29b444418","tid":1571182,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbf9876c15a186d0db52fdb7713bc41f9d54b2a","tid":1571182,"uid":51701,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"聽過有暴徒講話用膠水飛入閘, 真係痴撚線<br />\n會失民心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76bbf39c3871f61bdfb56cf270e84c1860d8cd7d","tid":1571182,"uid":55597,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"dbbf9876c15a186d0db52fdb7713bc41f9d54b2a","tid":1571182,"uid":51701,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"聽過有暴徒講話用膠水飛入閘, 真係痴撚線<br />\n會失民心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"5蚊KO一部機都幾抵"},{"pid":"59534c89a2356313b2b16a763a841126ce32158a","tid":1571182,"uid":214635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:00:12.000Z","msg":"尼仔好揪定南亞仔好揪d？"},{"pid":"a31ff3885d60805457fb13c459842be28f6a979b","tid":1571182,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76bbf39c3871f61bdfb56cf270e84c1860d8cd7d","tid":1571182,"uid":55597,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"dbbf9876c15a186d0db52fdb7713bc41f9d54b2a","tid":1571182,"uid":51701,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"聽